{"tid":868540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"愛情喺呢個世代係咗已經變咗質","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T16:23:25.000Z","uid":208132,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e91b7665e01073c3fd1ce32e47bb76065c527da","tid":868540,"uid":208132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"愛情，唔係應該始終如一。拍拖，唔係應該以結婚為前題架咩。<br />\n<br />\n點解而家呢個世代，可以有咁多出軌，綠帽嘅事，到底班扑街視愛情為何物？<br />\n<br />\n點解而家啲小朋友 中學生可以識三四日，一兩個月就開始拍拖，跟住光速咁散，然後一個月後又搵第二個，我唔明<br />\n<br />\n利申:而家女朋友係我嘅初戀，中學識咗五年，到而家拍咗八年拖<br />\n<br />\n到底係我思想守舊，定係呢個世代嘅愛情已經變咗質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時下世人問題，愛情應該始終如一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食屎啦，而家興自由戀愛"},{"pid":"b06b5cca393cf8707218997d826873349b2e29f2","tid":868540,"uid":199162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"可能以前所謂嘅「應該」都其實唔係真係應該 嗰啲只係以前嘅一套規則"},{"pid":"44b98d0ddb8b7b179b6ba248d5f8674129a0b4c9","tid":868540,"uid":2263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"我就係想同依加男朋友一生一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50992120a8b0f621b9a4d976f044ae4c40194b02","tid":868540,"uid":186888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44b98d0ddb8b7b179b6ba248d5f8674129a0b4c9","tid":868540,"uid":2263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"我就係想同依加男朋友一生一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e4fd2313c013b8a2e3f4557540e19801d26f32","tid":868540,"uid":208132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b06b5cca393cf8707218997d826873349b2e29f2","tid":868540,"uid":199162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"可能以前所謂嘅「應該」都其實唔係真係應該 嗰啲只係以前嘅一套規則"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"但係我都係覺得，一係唔拍，一拍就要搵一個可以行到最後嘅人"},{"pid":"b120dae775ab75112676d779bb2f4128529b0cec","tid":868540,"uid":22694,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"70年代： 愛情已經唔係好似以前咁<br />\n乜結婚唔係父母之命媒妁之言咩<br />\n點解家下啲人可以自己揀伴侶<br />\n<br />\n80年代：愛情已經唔係好似以前咁<br />\n乜唔係起碼拍拖先可以上床咩<br />\n點解家下啲人可以一夜情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代變，人會變<br />\n好正常啫"},{"pid":"250cda4da3948db75e99680deb30eae88bda2d2b","tid":868540,"uid":206896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"認同樓主，愛情而家啲人真係亂咁黎，散拖已經覺得唔太接受到，綠人個啲仆街更加不知所謂 <br />\n 利申： 冇比人帽過"},{"pid":"f0c8947c89119edbee5b4c7b45a011ad2b90b3fa","tid":868540,"uid":175539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"速食文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59a1eb21408a11f77cc2b49f54e5f58deb5fa7c","tid":868540,"uid":156326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係依家啲人慣左比藉口自己姐<br />\n有咩唔work只要話對方唔愛自己然後拍拍屁股就走"},{"pid":"b929b7fe7e495432c4246d5eb9e8549283e71ad1","tid":868540,"uid":208132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"到底佢地視愛情為何物"},{"pid":"4e93f4cc5d4c6e121767964d55412783bab2b0b3","tid":868540,"uid":206195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"個個拍緊拖嘅朋友都話拍住先，遲早都散啦。<br />\n我都唔明咁樣佢地拍拖做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af96c8a8efb7911d1eb412c160aed1a943ccc348","tid":868540,"uid":208132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e93f4cc5d4c6e121767964d55412783bab2b0b3","tid":868540,"uid":206195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"個個拍緊拖嘅朋友都話拍住先，遲早都散啦。<br />\n我都唔明咁樣佢地拍拖做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/won